template<typename T>
StreamableResult Aeryn::Williams::operator<< (  T const &  t,
Generic const &  u
) 
 

This is our operator<< It will accept anything as either parameter.

The template parameter on the lhs, means the lhs is always an exact match.

The Generic parameter on the rhs will accept anything, but the constructor requires an implicit conversion through an ellipsis, so ranks lowest of all options Finally, this is a template, so it ranks lower than a non-template.
